{"tid":191739,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"西班牙鬥牛過程","createTime":"2017-04-08T06:11:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T02:59:28.000Z","uid":104585,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"64dc448e118000561c193949105d7fac8f0f0f86","tid":191739,"uid":104585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T06:11:23.000Z","msg":"片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/flyagainla/videos/1426625164060759/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fflyagainla%2Fvideos%2F1426625164060759%2F&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FM6NGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=6c15da63\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/flyagainla/videos/1426625164060759/</a><br />\n<br />\n先把牛抓去關在一個黑暗的屋子裏，讓牠感到恐懼，而且不斷的激怒牠，讓牠憤怒無比。然後，把牛帶到鬥牛場。<br />\n<br />\n進場前，鬥牛士的助手先在牛背上插上一根尖銳的長槍 (arp&oacute;n)，讓牠又怕又痛又憤怒的繞着鬥牛場跑，但不能逃脫。<br />\n<br />\n接着，鬥牛士的助手再插上三四根尖銳的長槍 (pica)，有的深得穿透肺臟。等牛跑得筋疲力盡後，鬥牛士才出場，有近視又有色盲的牛以為鬥牛士的紅布是傷害牠的敵人，在觀眾的歡呼聲中，拚命往紅布亂撞。鬥牛士成功退場後，鬥牛士的助手又在牛背的傷口上，一根接一根的插上尖銳的長鈎 (banderillas)，讓四到六根有倒鈎的長鈎鈎在牠血淋淋的背部肌肉上，使得牛的每一步動作都讓牠痛得無法忍受。等到牛的行動有點遲緩，有垂頭等死的預兆，鬥牛士才又出場，趁牛痛得無法辨識無法逃避，拿起鋒利的長劍，一劍一劍的從牠背部刺向心臟，技術不好的幾乎都會失手，沒刺到心臟，刺到肺臟，使得鬥牛大量吐血。所以，很少有鬥牛是被一劍刺死的，通常都是慢慢的被牠肺臟出血的血液淹死的。<br />\n<br />\n然後，鬥牛士用短劍切斷牛的脊髓，但常常不能完全切斷，無法把牛殺死，只嚴重傷到牠的脊髓。<br />\n<br />\n最後，不管牛有沒有死透，把牠的耳朵割下來，拖着牠繞場走。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好撚無聊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食飽飯冇屎屙 <br />\n專登令隻牛驚同嬲 再整傷佢再玩9佢再殺左佢 <br />\n死唔斷氣個下最辛苦<br />\n隻牛到死個刻都唔知你呢班人做緊乜9<br />\n人類先係最殘忍最恐怖既物種"},{"pid":"15bbe0526a9af6114cba188fb9519510907f6f2e","tid":191739,"uid":90360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T06:25:59.000Z","msg":"嘩屌好殘忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"177f2952be09adff1f8a0efe8721d0147a10e5b0","tid":191739,"uid":24165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T06:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a71e7528c09389c6fd3f605e5ea150518cfec9b8","tid":191739,"uid":202469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:42:19.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原來咁撚血腥"},{"pid":"e11fb1ecac78151ae9e220d96cf4116319d9213f","tid":191739,"uid":104585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a71e7528c09389c6fd3f605e5ea150518cfec9b8","tid":191739,"uid":202469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:42:19.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原來咁撚血腥"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T00:13:35.000Z","msg":"冇啦啦睇兩年前既post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfbca7518bca56773bd3fd85ba0bc2e614fa82aa","tid":191739,"uid":202469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e11fb1ecac78151ae9e220d96cf4116319d9213f","tid":191739,"uid":104585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a71e7528c09389c6fd3f605e5ea150518cfec9b8","tid":191739,"uid":202469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:42:19.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原來咁撚血腥"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T00:13:35.000Z","msg":"冇啦啦睇兩年前既post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:59:28.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}